full_desc: Q0a. FRMDATE_D1D (D1D form date) cannot be blank
Q0a. FRMDATE_D1D (D1D form date) must be a date formatted mm/dd/yyyy or yyyy/mm/dd
test_logic: If FRMDATE_D1D is not mm/dd/yyyy or yyyy/mm/dd

full_desc: Q1. DSHEADCM (Head circumference (cm)) cannot be blank

short_desc: DSHEADCM must be an integer between 45-70, 777, or 888
full_desc: Q1. DSHEADCM (Head circumference (cm)) must be an integer between 45-70, 777 or 888
test_logic: IF DSHEADCM < 45 or (DSHEADCM > 70 and not in (777, 888))

Q5. DSCHROM (participant's chromosome diagnosis) cannot be blank
